MCB Bank Limited may disclose information collected from Users to trusted affiliates, independent contractors and business partners (If any) who will use the information for the purposes outlined above. We may also disclose aggregate, anonymous data based on information collected from Users, to investors and potential partners. Finally, we may transfer information collected in connection with a sale of our product and services.
